### Admin login
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@graphify.dev",
  "password": "admin1234"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("adminToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

### GET stats
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/admin/vectordb/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### POST reindex — 성공 (전체)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/admin/vectordb/reindex
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scope": "ALL"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("jobId", response.body.data.jobId);
%}

### GET job (폴링)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/admin/vectordb/jobs/{{jobId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### POST reindex — 실패 (선택 + 빈 targetIds)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/admin/vectordb/reindex
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scope": "SELECTED",
  "targetIds": []
}

### GET cleanup preview
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/admin/vectordb/cleanup/preview?olderThanDays=90&types=COMPANY,INSIGHT
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### DELETE cleanup — 성공
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/v1/admin/vectordb/cleanup
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "olderThanDays": 90,
  "types": ["COMPANY", "INSIGHT"]
}

### DELETE cleanup — 실패 (types 비움)
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/v1/admin/vectordb/cleanup
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "olderThanDays": 90,
  "types": []
}
